column5: I'm not one for writing big long reports so here's some shots from the last couple weeks.
nice. what were the fish on the sonar?

They are all splake tried jigging and drop shotting to them not even a nibble. Ran cookies and little cleo spoons. On our first pass double header.  Beat them up after that probably caught 20 fish in the next couple hours.
Cool.  Good job that would be a ton of fun.
